atg.ui.process.expression.ProcessExpressionGrammarExtension
public class ValidatedProfileMarkerGrammarExtension
extends ValidatedMarkerExpressionGrammar

Scenario Editor grammar extension for ProfileMarkerManager actions and expressions. This grammar extension provides the dynamic values for the key and value parameter selections.
